<FIRST>u i BC-Japan-Stocks     02-28 0026</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Japan-Stocks,0025</SECOND>
<HEAD>Stocks Down In Tokyo</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Nikkei Stock Average closed at 31,985.60, down
300.17 points, on the Tokyo Stock Exchange Wednesday.
</TEXT>
