race and endorsed Sawyer, but too late to have his name stricken
from the ballot.
   James C. Taylor, 59, former state legislator from Chicago's South
Side.
   Sheila A. Jones, 38, previous mayoral candidate and backer of
political extremist Lyndon LaRouche.
